Package: minoRityPower
Title: Power Analysis Tools for Minority Recruitment Interventions
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Sergey",
           family = "Kornilov",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "sergey.kornilov@biostochastics.com")
Description: Tools for analyzing and simulating power for minority recruitment
    interventions in clinical trials. Includes functions for analyzing 
    ClinicalTrials.gov data, estimating enrollment patterns, and conducting
    power analyses for multi-level trial designs.
